label: uncl5393
comment: Code qualifying the type of price multiplier.

values.label: Price adjustment coefficient
values.comment: Coefficient to be used in the price adjustment formula to calculate the revaluated price.

values.label: Escalation coefficient
values.comment: Coefficient to be used in the escalation formula to calculate the actual price.

values.label: Timesing factor
values.comment: Factor to be used in calculating the number of times a particular piece of work is repeated.

values.label: Cost markup multiplier - original cost
values.comment: Code specifying the cost mark-up multiplier at original cost.

values.label: Cost markup multiplier - retail cost
values.comment: Code specifying the cost mark-up multiplier at retail cost.
